MOTIVATED SELLERS!!  Seller is willing to contribute to a rate buy-down or Closing cost with an acceptable offer!
Welcome Home to this beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 Bath, House has open concept, Large Kitchen with Granite Countertops and Eating Bar. It has a Large Primary Bedroom with  A Garden Tub & Separate Shower.  Backyard is Kid & Pet Friendly with a Swing Set, The back Patio is covered and has retractable Sun Screens, Storage Building could make the Perfect She-Shed or Workshop , House is Move in Ready.  BUYER AND BUYER AGENT TO VERIFY ALL INFORMATION HEREIN.
